channel.title: Someone wanna help out accepting new SRL Members?
channel.description:
All they have to do is stick to the application and if you think they are good enough then you accept them into the user group.
Anyone fancy helping out? Cos i know Wizzup and Ben (I think) were doing it before
You need good judgement and not be bias in anyway, such as if you have known them before or they are your friend etc.
Thanks
Star
